data.description: This 4 bed home in located in a great location close to shopping and freeway access. Hidden inside a nice cul-de-sac, featuring granite counters with tumbled marble back splash, Tile in wet areas and wood look laminate through out. No carpet in entire home, great for pets. Large family room overlooks gourmet kitchen across breakfast bar. Great home office with French doors downstairs could function as 5th bedroom if needed. Upstairs you'll find a huge game-media room, 2 full baths, & 4 bedrooms including the master suite that features walk-in closet, separate shower & garden tub! Shed in back yard, Roof and HVAC less than 1 year old as well. Brand new water heater. And New Dishwasher. Solar panels that stay with the home reduce the electric to almost nothing to stay as cool as you like during hot Texas heat! Panels will be paid off at closing by seller.
